title: Microsoft Azure Traffic Manager: Probe State
agents: azure_v2
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the endpoint state of a Traffic Manager Profile.
 You can configure a CheckMk state in case endpoint state isn't OK
 using the "Azure Traffic Manager Probe State" rule.

discovery:
 One service is created for each traffic manager profile if
 required metric (maximum_ProbeAgentCurrentEndpointStateByProfileResourceId)
 is given.
